Then: President Trump lobbies
Republican members
of Congress to vote for the
revised health

00:28.762 --> 00:33.901 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
care replacement bill, warning
them their
reelection is at risk.

00:33.934 --> 00:39.806 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
