a better start.

00:39.840 --> 00:44.144 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JENNA SMITH, Runs Aquaponics
Greenhouse: Healthy
food is foundational to overall
health and

00:44.177 --> 00:45.879 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
