01:16.310 --> 01:22.249 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The federal appeals judge fended
off Democrats'
efforts today to ferret out his
views on hot-button

01:22.282 --> 01:24.084 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
issues.

01:24.117 --> 01:27.955 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
