York.

05:03.370 --> 05:08.575 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Last night, Republicans added a
provision
saying billions in county
Medicaid costs must

05:08.608 --> 05:11.411 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
