shortfall if
this amendment were to be
included.

05:34.234 --> 05:35.602 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

05:35.635 --> 05:37.470 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
CHUCK SCHUMER (D-NY), Minority
Leader: Their
bill is such a miss.

05:37.504 --> 05:42.275 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: Another key New
York Democrat,
Senate Minority Leader Chuck
Schumer, railed

05:42.309 --> 05:46.179 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
