squarely down Pennsylvania
Avenue.

05:46.213 --> 05:48.048 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
SEN.

05:48.081 --> 05:50.650 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
CHUCK SCHUMER: President Trump,
who has tried
to put his name on nearly
everything in his

05:50.684 --> 05:56.590 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
