here on the
Hill today to sell the bill to
House Republicans.

06:02.929 --> 06:05.065 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Make no mistake.

06:05.098 --> 06:06.866 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
