06:06.900 --> 06:10.837 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: Democrats hope
this health
care vote sinks some of these
Republicans

06:10.870 --> 06:14.074 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
