selling the opposite
message,

06:16.176 --> 06:19.746 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
DONALD TRUMP: There are going to
be adjustments
made, but I think we will get
the vote on

06:19.779 --> 06:20.747 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Thursday.

06:20.780 --> 06:22.115 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(CROSSTALK)

06:22.148 --> 06:24.050 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: ... that
Republicans need
this bill to survive.

06:24.084 --> 06:26.052 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
The vote remains very close at
this hour.

06:26.086 --> 06:28.221 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And tomorrow could be a key day.

06:28.255 --> 06:32.425 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
