07:06.259 --> 07:09.262 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: I spoke with a
spokeswoman
from House Speaker Paul Ryan's
office.

07:09.296 --> 07:11.531 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
