07:46.333 --> 07:49.436 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And then, Lisa,
as you just
reported, this afternoon, Lisa,
the White

07:49.469 --> 07:54.441 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
