Republicans
to try to persuade them.

07:54.474 --> 07:56.443 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
What are the arguments they're
using with
them?

07:56.476 --> 07:58.511 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
LISA DESJARDINS: This is part of
the full-court
press.

07:58.545 --> 08:00.747 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
