33:42.254 --> 33:43.722 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Welcome.

33:43.755 --> 33:46.491 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
I wonder if you could just tell
me a little
bit, what is going on here?

33:46.524 --> 33:49.561 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MATTHEW OLSEN, Former Director,
National Counterterrorism
Center: Well, it would appear
that, almost

33:49.594 --> 33:54.499 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
certainly, there is some new
intelligence
that the intelligence community
has gathered,

33:54.532 --> 34:00.038 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
whether on its own or from one
of our partners
in the region, that has given
the government,

34:00.071 --> 34:05.644 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
in particular the Department of
Homeland Security,
increased concern about the
possibility that

34:05.677 --> 34:10.548 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
