34:36.675 --> 34:38.510 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Is that right?

34:38.543 --> 34:42.380 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MATTHEW OLSEN: Well, we have
always had concern
about airports in this region,
and we have

34:42.414 --> 34:49.621 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
