the United
States.

34:53.825 --> 34:58.663 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But the truth is that the best
place to stop
a terrorist attack, a plot like
this, is at

34:58.697 --> 35:02.467 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
