where you can
have intelligence that allows
you to identify

35:02.500 --> 35:05.470 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
those individuals who are
responsible for
the plot.

35:05.503 --> 35:10.608 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
The last opportunity really is
at those airports,
and really you are at least
hoping that you're

35:10.642 --> 35:13.578 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
going to be able to stop a bomb
once it reaches
the airport gate.

35:13.611 --> 35:16.781 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: I mean, you
were in the
Obama administration when these
kinds of decisions

35:16.815 --> 35:19.484 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
