kind of intelligence
would trigger this kind of an
action?

35:23.955 --> 35:25.957 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
MATTHEW OLSEN: Sure.

35:25.991 --> 35:30.795 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
I mean, for one, this was a
source of constant
concern when I was at the
National Counterterrorism

35:30.829 --> 35:32.597 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Center.

35:32.630 --> 35:38.937 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
