United States.

35:40.772 --> 35:45.076 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, this has been an area of
real concern
because of the determination of
terrorist

35:45.110 --> 35:48.013 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
groups to blow up an airplane
bound for the
United States.

35:48.046 --> 35:52.684 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But the way this information may
well come
to light is a number of ways.

35:52.717 --> 35:58.456 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
One is through intercept of
communications
between terrorists talking about
something

35:58.490 --> 36:00.258 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
