-- come from
electronic surveillance or from
human sources.

36:09.634 --> 36:14.739 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
But, certainly, there is some
new information
from one of these types of
sources that then

36:14.773 --> 36:19.177 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
