36:29.654 --> 36:34.993 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Can you
explain the distinction
here between carry-on vs.
checked luggage?

36:35.026 --> 36:39.631 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
