36:45.570 --> 36:50.608 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
MATTHEW OLSEN: Well, there are
some instances
where we have seen devices --
think back to

36:50.642 --> 36:59.217 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
