37:00.718 --> 37:04.856 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So, the person had to have
access to the device
in order to detonate it.

37:04.889 --> 37:09.027 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, that is obviously a clear
distinction
between having checked luggage
and why there

37:09.060 --> 37:14.265 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
