somebody who has
got immediate access to --
potentially immediate

37:14.299 --> 37:18.470 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
access to a device because they
were able
to bring it on to an airplane,
as opposed

37:18.503 --> 37:20.305 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
