37:20.338 --> 37:24.142 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Does the fact
that the British
have also instituted a similar
ban, albeit

37:24.175 --> 37:27.846 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
