37:29.647 --> 37:34.719 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
MATTHEW OLSEN: Well, it
certainly does, at
least in the sense that the
United Kingdom

37:34.752 --> 37:41.993 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
and the United States work
incredibly closely
together on all these types of
issues and

37:42.026 --> 37:43.761 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
