37:43.795 --> 37:48.533 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It certainly suggests to me at
least that
the U.K. and the U.S. are in
lockstep in how

37:48.566 --> 37:53.037 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
