that has been in place -- that
has been in

38:22.634 --> 38:23.601 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
place for some time.

38:23.635 --> 38:24.836 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: All right.

