43:39.951 --> 43:43.754 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: A full-day
preschool program
with all this staff doesn't come
cheap.

43:43.788 --> 43:47.859 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
