that investment
is high.

44:03.274 --> 44:09.514 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
Every $1 spent on early
education returns
$13 in savings down the road.

44:09.547 --> 44:13.351 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
