soak it up as
they need it.

44:55.192 --> 44:56.961 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Wow.

44:56.994 --> 45:02.166 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
