operation.

45:04.101 --> 45:08.372 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JENNA SMITH: Healthy food is
foundational
to overall health and
well-being.

45:08.406 --> 45:14.946 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It's a very important component
to having
-- helping kids to grow up, pay
attention

45:14.979 --> 45:18.049 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
