classes.

45:45.610 --> 45:50.147 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
BEVERLY GRANT, Business Owner:
We have shifted
from food desert to food oasis.

45:50.181 --> 45:55.453 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Grant runs her
