BEVERLY GRANT: The blessing is
that Dr. Prado
had amazing listening ears and a
compassionate

46:04.328 --> 46:06.864 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
heart.

46:06.897 --> 46:13.304 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
