her, consider
that done.

46:18.676 --> 46:23.014 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: As Grant likes
to say, from
seed to stomach.

46:23.047 --> 46:27.418 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
